Perfeito! Abaixo está o seu script ajustado para gerar uma mensagem personalizada com a contagem detalhada de sequências seguidas para:

  • Cores, Paridade e Metades (de 10 a 20 repetições seguidas)

✅ Script Atualizado:

javascript
(async () => {
  const TOKEN = '8157540250:AAEVAE7YBfIaB1V8ZlEVF6xOUCj_NBaGBOg';
  const CHAT_ID = '-1002585818869';
  const ROULETTE_NAME = 'Auto Mega Roulette';

  const getColor = (n) => {
    if (n === 0) return 'green';
    const reds = [1, 3, 5, 7, 9, 12, 14, 16, 18, 19, 21, 23, 25, 27, 30, 32, 34, 36];
    return reds.includes(n) ? 'red' : 'black';
  };
  const getParity = (n) => n === 0 ? 'none' : (n % 2 === 0 ? 'even' : 'odd');
  const getHalf = (n) => n === 0 ? 'none' : (n <= 18 ? 'low' : 'high');
  const getDozen = (n) => n === 0 ? 'none' : (n <= 12 ? '1st' : n <= 24 ? '2nd' : '3rd');
  const getColumn = (n) => n === 0 ? 'none' : (n % 3 === 1 ? 'col1' : n % 3 === 2 ? 'col2' : 'col3');

  // Conta quantas vezes sequências exatas de tamanhos variados ocorrem
  const countStreaksByLength = (arr, min, max) => {
    const counts = {};
    for (let len = min; len <= max; len++) {
      counts[len] = 0;
    }
    for (let i = 0; i < arr.length; i++) {
      let current = arr[i];
      let streak = 1;
      for (let j = i + 1; j < arr.length && arr[j] === current; j++) {
        streak++;
        if (streak >= min && streak <= max) {
          counts[streak]++;
          i = j;
        }
        if (streak > max) break;
      }
    }
    return counts;
  };

  const sendTelegramMessage = async (text) => {
    const url = `https://api.telegram.org/bot${TOKEN}/sendMessage`;
    await fetch(url, {
      method: 'POST',
      headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
      body: JSON.stringify({
        chat_id: CHAT_ID,
        text,
        parse_mode: 'Markdown'
      })
    });
  };

  const analyze = () => {
    console.clear();
    const results = [...document.querySelectorAll('.cell__circle .cell__result')]
      .slice(0, 200)
      .map(el => parseInt(el.textContent.trim()))
      .filter(n => !isNaN(n));

    const colors = results.map(getColor);
    const parity = results.map(getParity);
    const halves = results.map(getHalf);
    const dozens = results.map(getDozen);
    const columns = results.map(getColumn);

    const coresStreaks = countStreaksByLength(colors, 10, 20);
    const paridadeStreaks = countStreaksByLength(parity, 10, 20);
    const metadeStreaks = countStreaksByLength(halves, 10, 20);
    const duziaStreaks = countStreaksByLength(dozens, 6, 12);
    const colunaStreaks = countStreaksByLength(columns, 6, 12);

    const formatSection = (title, data) => {
      return `*${title}*\n` + Object.entries(data).map(([len, count]) => `${len} - ${count}`).join('\n') + '\n';
    };

    const msg =
      `🎰 *${ROULETTE_NAME}*\n\n` +
      formatSection('🎨 Cores seguidas', coresStreaks) + '\n' +
      formatSection('⚖️ Paridades seguidas', paridadeStreaks) + '\n' +
      formatSection('📈 Metades seguidas', metadeStreaks) + '\n' +
      formatSection('📦 Dúzias seguidas', duziaStreaks) + '\n' +
      formatSection('📊 Colunas seguidas', colunaStreaks);

    console.log(msg);
    sendTelegramMessage(msg);
  };

  analyze(); // execução imediata
  setInterval(analyze, 5 * 60 * 60 * 500); // a cada 2:30 horas
})();

Agora ele conta apenas sequências com exatamente o tamanho solicitado.

javascript
(async () => {
  const TOKEN = '8157540250:AAEVAE7YBfIaB1V8ZlEVF6xOUCj_NBaGBOg';
  const CHAT_ID = '-1002585818869';
  const ROULETTE_NAME = 'Auto Mega Roulette';

  const getColor = (n) => {
    if (n === 0) return 'green';
    const reds = [1, 3, 5, 7, 9, 12, 14, 16, 18, 19, 21, 23, 25, 27, 30, 32, 34, 36];
    return reds.includes(n) ? 'red' : 'black';
  };
  const getParity = (n) => n === 0 ? 'none' : (n % 2 === 0 ? 'even' : 'odd');
  const getHalf = (n) => n === 0 ? 'none' : (n <= 18 ? 'low' : 'high');
  const getDozen = (n) => n === 0 ? 'none' : (n <= 12 ? '1st' : n <= 24 ? '2nd' : '3rd');
  const getColumn = (n) => n === 0 ? 'none' : (n % 3 === 1 ? 'col1' : n % 3 === 2 ? 'col2' : 'col3');

  // Conta quantas vezes ocorrem sequências EXATAS (sem sobreposição) de cada tamanho
  const countExactStreaksByLength = (arr, min, max) => {
    const counts = {};
    for (let len = min; len <= max; len++) {
      counts[len] = 0;
    }

    let i = 0;
    while (i < arr.length) {
      const current = arr[i];
      let streak = 1;

      for (let j = i + 1; j < arr.length && arr[j] === current; j++) {
        streak++;
      }

      if (streak >= min && streak <= max) {
        counts[streak]++;
        i += streak; // pular a sequência inteira
      } else {
        i++;
      }
    }

    return counts;
  };

  const sendTelegramMessage = async (text) => {
    const url = `https://api.telegram.org/bot${TOKEN}/sendMessage`;
    await fetch(url, {
      method: 'POST',
      headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
      body: JSON.stringify({
        chat_id: CHAT_ID,
        text,
        parse_mode: 'Markdown'
      })
    });
  };

  const analyze = () => {
    console.clear();
    const results = [...document.querySelectorAll('.cell__circle .cell__result')]
      .slice(0, 200)
      .map(el => parseInt(el.textContent.trim()))
      .filter(n => !isNaN(n));

    const colors = results.map(getColor);
    const parity = results.map(getParity);
    const halves = results.map(getHalf);
    const dozens = results.map(getDozen);
    const columns = results.map(getColumn);

    const coresStreaks = countExactStreaksByLength(colors, 10, 20);
    const paridadeStreaks = countExactStreaksByLength(parity, 10, 20);
    const metadeStreaks = countExactStreaksByLength(halves, 10, 20);
    const duziaStreaks = countExactStreaksByLength(dozens, 6, 12);
    const colunaStreaks = countExactStreaksByLength(columns, 6, 12);

    const formatSection = (title, data) => {
      return `*${title}*\n` + Object.entries(data).map(([len, count]) => `${len} - ${count}`).join('\n') + '\n';
    };

    const msg =
      `🎰 *${ROULETTE_NAME}*\n\n` +
      formatSection('🎨 Cores seguidas', coresStreaks) + '\n' +
      formatSection('⚖️ Paridades seguidas', paridadeStreaks) + '\n' +
      formatSection('📈 Metades seguidas', metadeStreaks) + '\n' +
      formatSection('📦 Dúzias seguidas', duziaStreaks) + '\n' +
      formatSection('📊 Colunas seguidas', colunaStreaks);

    console.log(msg);
    sendTelegramMessage(msg);
  };

  analyze(); // execução imediata
  setInterval(analyze, 5 * 60 * 60 * 500); // a cada 2:30 horas
})();

(async () => {
  const TOKEN = '8157540250:AAEVAE7BfIaB1V8ZlEVF6xOUCj_NBaGBOg';

    if (n === 0) return 'green';

    return reds.includes(n) ? 'red' : 'black';
  };
  const getParity = (n) => n === 0 ? 'none' : (n % 2 === 0 ? 'even' : 'odd');
  const getHalf = (n) => n === 0 ? 'none' : (n <= 18 ? 'low' : 'high');
  const getDozen = (n) => n === 0 ? 'none' : (n <= 12 ? '1st' : n <= 24 ? '2nd' : '3rd');
  const getColumn = (n) => n === 0 ? 'none' : (n % 3 === 1 ? 'col1' : n % 3 === 2 ? 'col2' : 'col3');

      counts[len] = 0;
    }

    let i = 0;
    while (i < arr.length) {
      const value = arr[i];
      let streak = 1;

      for (let j = i + 1; j < arr.length && arr[j] === value; j++) {
        streak++;
      }

      if (streak >= min && streak <= max) {
        counts[streak]++;
        i += streak;
      } else {
        i++;
      }
    }

    return counts;
  };

      body: JSON.stringify({
        chat_id: CHAT_ID,
        text,
        parse_mode: 'Markdown'
      })
    });
  };

  const formatSection = (title, data) => {
    return `*${title}*\n` + Object.entries(data).map(([len, count]) => `${len} - ${count}`).join('\n') + '\n';

      .slice(0, 200)
      .map(el => parseInt(el.textContent.trim()))

    const colors = results.map(getColor);
    const parity = results.map(getParity);
    const halves = results.map(getHalf);
    const dozens = results.map(getDozen);
    const columns = results.map(getColumn);

🚀 SCRIPT ADAPTADO (com geração de imagem)

Aqui vai a versão adaptada que gera a imagem no canvas e envia para o Telegram:

js
(async () => {
  const TOKEN = '8157540250:AAEVAE7YBfIaB1V8ZlEVF6xOUCj_NBaGBOg';
  const CHAT_ID = '-1002512280525';
  const ROULETTE_NAME = 'Mega Roulette';
  const INTERVALO_MS = 5 * 60 * 60 * 500; // 2:30 horas

  const getColor = (n) => {
    if (n === 0) return 'green';
    const reds = [1, 3, 5, 7, 9, 12, 14, 16, 18, 19, 21, 23, 25, 27, 30, 32, 34, 36];
    return reds.includes(n) ? 'red' : 'black';
  };
  const getParity = (n) => n === 0 ? 'none' : (n % 2 === 0 ? 'even' : 'odd');
  const getHalf = (n) => n === 0 ? 'none' : (n <= 18 ? 'low' : 'high');
  const getDozen = (n) => n === 0 ? 'none' : (n <= 12 ? '1st' : n <= 24 ? '2nd' : '3rd');
  const getColumn = (n) => n === 0 ? 'none' : (n % 3 === 1 ? 'col1' : n % 3 === 2 ? 'col2' : 'col3');

  const countExactStreaksByLength = (arr, min, max) => {
    const counts = {};
    for (let len = min; len <= max; len++) {
      counts[len] = 0;
    }
    let i = 0;
    while (i < arr.length) {
      const value = arr[i];
      let streak = 1;
      for (let j = i + 1; j < arr.length && arr[j] === value; j++) {
        streak++;
      }
      if (streak >= min && streak <= max) {
        counts[streak]++;
        i += streak;
      } else {
        i++;
      }
    }
    return counts;
  };

  const generateImage = (dataSections) => {
    const canvas = document.createElement('canvas');
    const ctx = canvas.getContext('2d');
    const width = 600;
    const lineHeight = 24;
    const margin = 20;
    const sectionSpacing = 10;
    const sectionCount = Object.keys(dataSections).length;
    const totalLines = Object.values(dataSections).reduce((sum, obj) => sum + Object.keys(obj).length + 1, 0);

    canvas.width = width;
    canvas.height = margin * 2 + (lineHeight + sectionSpacing) * totalLines;

    // fundo branco
    ctx.fillStyle = '#ffffff';
    ctx.fillRect(0, 0, canvas.width, canvas.height);

    // título
    ctx.fillStyle = '#000000';
    ctx.font = 'bold 22px Arial';
    ctx.fillText(`🎰 ${ROULETTE_NAME}`, margin, margin + lineHeight);

    ctx.font = '16px Arial';
    let y = margin + lineHeight * 2;

    for (const [section, values] of Object.entries(dataSections)) {
      ctx.fillStyle = '#000000';
      ctx.fillText(`📌 ${section}`, margin, y);
      y += lineHeight;

      ctx.fillStyle = '#333333';
      for (const [len, count] of Object.entries(values)) {
        ctx.fillText(`${len} ➜ ${count}`, margin + 20, y);
        y += lineHeight;
      }

      y += sectionSpacing;
    }

    return new Promise((resolve) => {
      canvas.toBlob(blob => resolve(blob), 'image/png');
    });
  };

  const sendTelegramImage = async (imageBlob) => {
    const formData = new FormData();
    formData.append('chat_id', CHAT_ID);
    formData.append('photo', imageBlob, 'roleta.png');

    const url = `https://api.telegram.org/bot${TOKEN}/sendPhoto`;
    await fetch(url, {
      method: 'POST',
      body: formData
    });
  };

  const analyze = async () => {
    const results = [...document.querySelectorAll('.cell__circle .cell__result')]
      .slice(0, 200)
      .map(el => parseInt(el.textContent.trim()))
      .filter(n => !isNaN(n));

    const colors = results.map(getColor);
    const parity = results.map(getParity);
    const halves = results.map(getHalf);
    const dozens = results.map(getDozen);
    const columns = results.map(getColumn);

    const dataSections = {
      '🎨 Cores seguidas': countExactStreaksByLength(colors, 10, 20),
      '⚖️ Paridades seguidas': countExactStreaksByLength(parity, 10, 20),
      '📈 Metades seguidas': countExactStreaksByLength(halves, 10, 20),
      '📦 Dúzias seguidas': countExactStreaksByLength(dozens, 6, 12),
      '📊 Colunas seguidas': countExactStreaksByLength(columns, 6, 12)
    };

    const imageBlob = await generateImage(dataSections);
    await sendTelegramImage(imageBlob);
  };

  analyze();
  setInterval(analyze, INTERVALO_MS);
})();

js
(async () => {
  const TOKEN = '8157540250:AAEVAE7BfIaB1V8ZlEVF6xOUCj_NBaGBOg';
  const CHAT_ID = '-1002512280525';
  const ROULETTE_NAME = 'Mega Roulette';
  const INTERVALO_MS = 5 * 60 * 60 * 500;

  const getColor = (n) => {
    if (n === 0) return 'green';
    const reds = [1, 3, 5, 7, 9, 12, 14, 16, 18, 19, 21, 23, 25, 27, 30, 32, 34, 36];
    return reds.includes(n) ? 'red' : 'black';
  };
  const getParity = (n) => n === 0 ? 'none' : (n % 2 === 0 ? 'even' : 'odd');
  const getHalf = (n) => n === 0 ? 'none' : (n <= 18 ? 'low' : 'high');
  const getDozen = (n) => n === 0 ? 'none' : (n <= 12 ? '1st' : n <= 24 ? '2nd' : '3rd');
  const getColumn = (n) => n === 0 ? 'none' : (n % 3 === 1 ? 'col1' : n % 3 === 2 ? 'col2' : 'col3');

  const countExactStreaksByLength = (arr, min, max) => {
    const counts = {};
    for (let len = min; len <= max; len++) counts[len] = 0;
    let i = 0;
    while (i < arr.length) {
      const value = arr[i];
      let streak = 1;
      for (let j = i + 1; j < arr.length && arr[j] === value; j++) streak++;
      if (streak >= min && streak <= max) {
        counts[streak]++;
        i += streak;
      } else i++;
    }
    return counts;
  };

  const generateImage = (dataSections) => {
    const canvas = document.createElement('canvas');
    const ctx = canvas.getContext('2d');
    const width = 700;
    const lineHeight = 32;
    const margin = 40;
    const sectionSpacing = 20;
    const sectionCount = Object.keys(dataSections).length;
    const totalLines = Object.values(dataSections).reduce((sum, obj) => sum + Object.keys(obj).length + 1, 0);

    canvas.width = width;
    canvas.height = margin + lineHeight * totalLines + sectionSpacing * sectionCount + 40;

    // Fundo moderno escuro
    ctx.fillStyle = '#1e1e1e';
    ctx.fillRect(0, 0, canvas.width, canvas.height);

    // Título
    ctx.fillStyle = '#ffffff';
    ctx.font = 'bold 26px Arial';
    ctx.fillText(`🎰 ${ROULETTE_NAME} • Análise Automática`, margin, 50);

    ctx.font = '18px Arial';
    let y = 90;

    for (const [section, values] of Object.entries(dataSections)) {
      // Seção em destaque
      ctx.fillStyle = '#f1c40f'; // amarelo
      ctx.fillText(section, margin, y);
      y += lineHeight;

      // Itens da seção
      ctx.fillStyle = '#ecf0f1'; // cinza claro
      for (const [len, count] of Object.entries(values)) {
        if (count > 0) {
          ctx.fillText(`➡️ ${len} vezes ➜ ${count}`, margin + 30, y);
          y += lineHeight;
        }
      }

      y += sectionSpacing;
    }

    return new Promise((resolve) => {
      canvas.toBlob(blob => resolve(blob), 'image/png');
    });
  };

  const sendTelegramImage = async (imageBlob) => {
    const formData = new FormData();
    formData.append('chat_id', CHAT_ID);
    formData.append('photo', imageBlob, 'roleta.png');

    const url = `https://api.telegram.org/bot${TOKEN}/sendPhoto`;
    await fetch(url, {
      method: 'POST',
      body: formData
    });
  };

  const analyze = async () => {
    const results = [...document.querySelectorAll('.cell__circle .cell__result')]
      .slice(0, 200)
      .map(el => parseInt(el.textContent.trim()))
      .filter(n => !isNaN(n));

    const colors = results.map(getColor);
    const parity = results.map(getParity);
    const halves = results.map(getHalf);
    const dozens = results.map(getDozen);
    const columns = results.map(getColumn);

    const dataSections = {
      '🎨 Cores seguidas': countExactStreaksByLength(colors, 10, 20),
      '⚖️ Paridades seguidas': countExactStreaksByLength(parity, 10, 20),
      '📈 Metades seguidas': countExactStreaksByLength(halves, 10, 20),
      '📦 Dúzias seguidas': countExactStreaksByLength(dozens, 6, 12),
      '📊 Colunas seguidas': countExactStreaksByLength(columns, 6, 12)
    };

    const imageBlob = await generateImage(dataSections);
    await sendTelegramImage(imageBlob);
  };

  analyze();
  setInterval(analyze, INTERVALO_MS);
})();

✅ SCRIPT COMPLETO COM ENVIO DE IMAGEM

Certifique-se de hospedar a imagem em um link direto acessível publicamente. Aqui estou usando um caminho de exemplo (IMAGE_URL). Substitua pelo link correto após fazer o upload da imagem (por exemplo, no Imgur, Discord, ou hospedagem própria).

javascript
(async () => {
  const TOKEN = '8157540250:AAEVAE7YBfIaB1V8ZlEVF6xOUCj_NBaGBOg';
  const CHAT_ID = '-1002512280525';
  const ROULETTE_NAME = 'Mega Roulette';
  const INTERVALO_MS = 5 * 60 * 60 * 500; // 2:30h
  const IMAGE_URL = 'https://example.com/sua-imagem.png'; // Substitua pelo link real da imagem

  const sendTelegramImage = async (imageUrl, caption = '') => {
    const url = `https://api.telegram.org/bot${TOKEN}/sendPhoto`;
    await fetch(url, {
      method: 'POST',
      headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
      body: JSON.stringify({
        chat_id: CHAT_ID,
        photo: imageUrl,
        caption,
        parse_mode: 'Markdown'
      })
    });
  };

  const analyze = () => {
    console.clear();
    const caption = `🎰 *${ROULETTE_NAME}*\nAnálise atualizada automática.`;
    sendTelegramImage(IMAGE_URL, caption);
  };

  analyze(); // execução imediata
  setInterval(analyze, INTERVALO_MS); // execução recorrente
})();
